    "name": "Effect: Invoke the Leviathan",
    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Invoke the Leviathan]</p>\n<p>you transform into a Gargantuan ijtikri leviathan battle form.</p>\n<p>You gain the following statistics and abilities.</p><ul><li>AC = 22 + your level. Ignore your armor's check penalty and Speed reduction.</li><li>10 temporary Hit Points.</li><li>Speed 10 feet, fly 40 feet, swim 60 feet</li><li>The following unarmed melee attacks. You're trained with this attack, and your attack modifier is +25. This attack is Strength based. If your unarmed attack modifier is higher, you can use it instead. <strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> tentacle (backswing, grapple, reach 30 feet), Damage 3d10+15 bludgeoning; <strong>Area Fire</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> wail (@Template[type:cone|distance:60]), Damage 3d10+15 sonic (basic Reflex save versus the higher of your class DC or spell DC)</li><li>Acrobatics modifier of +15 and Athletics modifier of +25, unless your own modifiers are higher.</li></ul>"
        },
